gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 112, Thunder 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Thunder, 112-105. Anthony Davis led the way for the Lakers with 27 points, 15 rebounds and five assists, while LeBron James added 25 points (12-20 FG), seven rebounds and six assists in the victory. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander tallied 24 points and six assists for the Thunder in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 20-21 on the season, while the Thunder snap a four-game win streak as they fall to 27-12.
